Feature: set up user profile

	As a user
	I want to be able to set up my user 	profile
	So that I can modify my nickname, email and 	phone number on the app

Acceptance criteria:
	*The user must confirm password to make 	 changes
	*Company members require authorization from 	 their employer to make changes
	
	Scenario: Andrea wants to change her nickname
	 Given she clicks on “Profile” button
	 And clicks on the pencil picture for editing
	 When she writes a different nickname and 	 saves it
	 Then a message saying “Changes saved 	 correctly” appears
